Module Minesweeper

Package swe.group_nine.controller

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Controller
    Controller interface implements the game model used as a controller
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractController
    The AbstractController class implements the controller as an abstract model for the minesweeper game
    GameController
    The GameController class implements the control logic for the minesweeper game.
    Square
    The Square class implements logic for the individual square of the Minesweeper game.
    Timer
    The Timer class starts a counter when the game starts so the user knows how long it took them to complete the game.
